lang#en:|虚拟桌宠模拟器模组同步or链接辅助工具，运行此工具将创建软连接（Junction），以达到不需要复制or移动即可让管理器在离线或非Steam启动状态识别到模组的目的！直接打开所在文件夹并运行vpet_sync。要断开连接，运行vpet_sync_break。#VPet simulator MOD synchronization or link assist tool. Running this tool will create a junction to achieve the goal of allowing the manager to recognize the module offline or non Steam startup state without the need for copying or moving! Open the folder directly and run vpet_sync. To disconnect, run vpet_sync_break. :|Core#Core:|
